title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 6 categories of Response on the x axis representing 5 groups: 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018.
Averaging these 5 groups, the highest category is found for Response Yes if I believe the reviews are authentic with a mean value of 25.2.
Followed by Yes if there are multiple customer reviews to read with a mean value of 22.0.
The lowest category is observed at No I am often skeptical about online reviews that has a mean value of 8.2
showing a difference of 101.8% with the maximum value.

In case of Yes for some types of businesses no for others, 2014 shows more dominance than any other Response with a value 34.0 and it has the lowest value 0.0 in Yes always.  However, 2015 is the second impactful group, and it has the highest value 27.0 for Response Yes if I believe the reviews are authentic and the lowest 4.0 in case of No I don't trust reviews at all.
